{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But before I get to this, so as Hitler became-- you know, had more power and more power, all the other dignitaries also had houses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had what we called villa, like a country home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the streets that I had to walk down to go to school, there was Himmler, who was known for-- he was Minister of-- no, that was Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Himmler was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] troopers, the black-- you know, the black troopers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS, the stormtrooper, head of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was Stuermer and Roehm, who was-- and they all had their houses along this row.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Roehm was assassinated by the Nazi themselves, I think for political reasons, or also because it was later said he was homosexual.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was also talk that he had planned to overthrow, some kind of a putsch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, so when-- when Hitler came out from the house, by later on, of course, the limousine waited.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then people started-- and the women were the most fanatic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were thousands of women lined up on our side of the street waiting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, of course, they had barricades and so on that you could hardly walk by, waiting for hours for Hitler to come out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the women were the most fanatic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The women really were, I guess, the most fanatic supporters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I guess we always knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I guess when-- I don't know when he moved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, the historical thing is that-- I guess the putsch was-- now I'm not sure if it was 1922 or 1923.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the first attempt to overthrow the then Bavarian government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hitler was at that time imprisoned.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
